snippet.title: Duels of Fortune: EVO 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
The Duels of Fortune trailer that was shown off at EVO 2022 during the indie showcase! Huge thank you to the folks at EVO for giving us this opportunity!

DoF Discord: https://discord.gg/Y8HxEWB
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Toast_Hatter
